title: Super Bowl 50 preview
itunes:title: Super Bowl 50 preview
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Conor Orr – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL, including 49ers quarterback Colin Kaepernick reportedly showing interest in playing for the Jets, and the latest on DeMarco Murray’s uncertain future with the Eagles. Then, the heroes turn their attention to Super Bowl 50 with Super Bowl Superlatives, Bold predictions, game picks, and who the heroes think will take home the title of MVP on Sunday. Plus, a Super Bowl edition of “Orr you kidding me?”.
